  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>Are you intrigued and motivated by art, design and media? This course will offer you opportunities to explore, develop and test your creativity even further.</p>
<p>Using established approaches to your teaching, learning and assessment, this course is perfect if you seek practical study over a more academic study route.<br /><br /></p>]]></mainContent>
